      "span_text": "Consistent with a previous report  , we found that in cells from the CA1-CA3 region of the rat hippocampus only 7% of the Kv1.1 transcripts undergo I400V editing (7 out of 100 clones), much less than the 50% editing found in the LGN neurons."
